===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪkə(r)|-ɪkə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A short [[moment]].
# An unsteady [[flash]] of light.

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{intransitive}} To keep going on and off; to [[appear]] and [[disappear]] for short moments; to [[flutter]].
